```yaml id="dwvc79"
breaks:
  - DSH checkout -> WLT payment session
  - DSH outbox worker -> WLT COD record
  - WLT -> DSH payment-session event callback
  - Docker runtime smoke
  - أي end-to-end يدّعي DSH/WLT integration
```
 
**المعالجة الصحيحة:**
 
```yaml id="knmjb3"
add_to_runtime_env:
  WLT_DSH_SERVICE_TOKEN: dev-wlt-dsh-service-token
  DSH_WLT_SERVICE_TOKEN: dev-dsh-wlt-service-token
 
compose_wlt_api_env:
  WLT_DSH_SERVICE_TOKEN: ${WLT_DSH_SERVICE_TOKEN}
 
compose_dsh_api_env:
  WLT_DSH_SERVICE_TOKEN: ${WLT_DSH_SERVICE_TOKEN}
